{"tid":113251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國計劃今年發射全球首個「夜光遙感衛星」","createTime":"2017-02-08T19:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T04:22:14.000Z","uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"faadbfec2572bee3880091ab28cdc19a49f1af08","tid":113251,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:15:51.000Z","msg":"中國航天科技集團2月8日公布，計劃在2017年發射全球首顆專業夜光遙感衛星「珞珈一號」01星，在2019年發射「珞珈一號」02星，用以驗證雷達衛星多角度成像模式。<br />\n<br />\n「珞珈一號」01星搭載了高靈敏度夜光相機，其精度將達到地面分辨率100米。夜間可看見長江上所有亮燈的大橋，獲取精度高於當前美國衛星的夜景圖片。<br />\n<br />\n「珞珈一號」02星由武漢大學與中國航天科技集團聯合研發。中國航天科技集團五院衛星型號總設計師張慶君說，該星是滿足1:50000測繪精度的多角度成像新體制雷達衛星，衛星設計具有條帶、聚束、多角度、雙基地等成像模式，對中國雷達衛星和衛星測繪創新發展具有重要意義。"},{"pid":"54124228c6b7a8bcbddb40b26f96fd627b7d61f5","tid":113251,"uid":79519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:22:57.000Z","msg":"射到一地都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a265524f7bc800513fe61b638d78e1c871fcb0e4","tid":113251,"uid":65847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:25:38.000Z","msg":"太空垃圾"},{"pid":"0c97c6e09483cde76854f2b200a3be6bdc11225a","tid":113251,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:32:29.000Z","msg":"美國衛星的夜景相機 <br />\nNikon d4s 400mm f2.8E<br />\n<img src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2016/06/nikongeariss-800x572.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2Fnikongeariss-800x572.jpg&h=fa8fda6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a304d5fda9158dba78cf5c85c27496141f35ead6","tid":113251,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T20:27:27.000Z","msg":"射上天，失去聯絡"},{"pid":"9cc408714a93ab9343bc2d38638965b3a8c427cc","tid":113251,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T02:02:00.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"e5ff9fccac3ddf7126876cf003f630824a2